ery 8 hours at 00:00, 08:00, and 16:00 UTC using the Premium Index formula. The funding rate is capped at ±0.75% per payment to prevent extreme volatility. Long positions pay short positions when funding is positive, reflecting market sentiment toward RUNE's price direction. Bybit's unified trading account allows seamless capital allocation between spot RUNE holdings and perpetual positions for delta-neutral strategies."}]]}],"$Lf",["$L10","$L11","$L12"],"$L13"]}],"$L14"]}]]}]
